  "prompt": "How much does a 60-minute massage cost in Houston, TX?",
  "response": "The cost of a 60-minute massage in Houston, TX, can vary widely depending on several factors such as the type of massage, the location, the experience of the therapist, and whether it's at a spa or a wellness center. On average, you can expect to pay between $60 to $120 for a one-hour massage. Some high-end spas may charge more, while budget options or massage chains may offer services at lower rates, sometimes starting around $50. Always check for any promotions or package deals, which can also influence pricing.",
